---
title: Quick Seared Double Salmon & Veggie Couscous Bowl with Herby Mayo & Parsley
description: Fibre-rich, colourful, nutritious, flavoursome – these are just a few of the ways we can describe this amazing couscous dish. Topped with fresh and flavourful salmon with a drizzle of herby mayo, don’t be too surprised when your tastebuds love it just as much as your body does!

*We’ve replaced the basil in this recipe with parsley due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
